Two points to clarify why the SoW potion is so expensive:

1) It takes between 8 to 12pp to produce the potion

2) The SoW spell does not work in some caverns. I frequent Paludal Caverns and Shadow Haven often. Since you CAN'T cast SoW in those zones it becomes necessary to leave the zone to get SoW. The potions come in handy when you find yourself trying to outrun a mob of bandits.

So to all you whiners, I hope you find yourself in a situation like the one I described in item 2.

